  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We support 10 students with disabilities for a school year, which are deficient in the emotional, intellectual, language, motor skills, vision and hearing areas. . In the Special Child Care Centre, they offer group and individual therapies that allow them to develop their potential in school, social and family areas. Attend school Monday through Friday, from 8:00 until 13:00. Your parents and / or guardians are committed to rehabilitation, however, find it difficult to pay tuition.</narrative>
  </description>
